commit.message:
Use CMAKE_FULL_*DIR in pkg-config file

Otherwise, it doesn't work if these directories are not subdirectories
of the prefix.
Build deb packages using debian stable
Remove executable bits from source files
Bump version and update RPM spec

Debian package fixes

- compatibility with debian
- remove .c files
- remove -tools package
- update URLs

Add OPTIMIZE option

- By default, build with -O3
- If user specifies -DOPTIMIZE=<N>, build with -O<N>
- If user specifies -DOPTIMIZE=DEFAULT, don't touch -O

Update cmake files for distros packaging

Signed-off-by: Jaroslav karvada <jskarvad@redhat.com>
Extract project version from git tag
Added rpm spec compatible with openSUSE 15.4
Added package build workflow using github actions

android: Fix building for Android/Termux

There is no bcmp and bcopy functions on Android
Fixes "error: undefined reference to 'bcmp'" and "error: undefined reference to 'bcopy'" linking errors.
